txt.en: Sûhalar captains can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar captains on top of the Rammas.
'There are two Easterling captains upon the Out-wall. They both must be defeated if we are to retake the Rammas!'
Sûhalar captains can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar captains on top of the Rammas.
Easterlings have invaded the northern Rammas and it is up to you to see them off the Out-wall.
